(16,"wc-admin-optimizing-the-checkout-flow","info","en_US","Optimizing the checkout flow","It\'s crucial to get your store\'s checkout as smooth as possible to avoid losing sales. Let\'s take a look at how you can optimize the checkout experience for your shoppers.","{}","pending","woocommerce.com","2021-08-09 15:26:34",NULL,0,"plain","",0,"info"),
